Preheat an oven to 450 degrees F (230 degrees C). Position oven rack in the center of the oven. Combine cauliflower, carrots, onion, and oil in bowl and toss until the vegetables are well coated. Season with salt and pepper. Transfer to a baking sheet and spread into a single layer. Bake in the preheated oven until golden brown and tender, 30 to 40 minutes.